methods.name: New
methods.logic: Creates a new Number object.

methods.name: ValueOf
methods.logic: Returns the double value of the Number object.

methods.name: Cast
methods.logic: Casts a Value to a NumberObject, with an assertion in debug mode.

methods.name: CheckCast
methods.logic: Performs a type check to ensure the cast is valid. Only enabled when V8_ENABLE_CHECKS is defined.
